### Welcome to  core-moos.
Here you can download the core-moos project. The main project page is at http://www.robots.ox.ac.uk~/pnewman/themoos
tagline: A very light weight, easy to use middleware. core-moos is what you want for low hassle interprocess comms.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
